---
title: Bayou-Spiced Rockfish with Southern Succotash and Crispy Roasted Potatoes
description: One Southern-inspired dish, coming up! We combined one of our favorite white-fleshed fishes with a mild Cajun spice and served it alongside a colorful succotash of corn, green beans, and tomatoes. And of course there’s some potatoes thrown in there, too. A sprinkle of chives gives this dish a magazine- worthy finish.
